                    <span>What an awesome book. An excellent choice for anyone that wants a detailed understanding of Server 2003. I think this book is well organized and easier to read than most books ive read on this subject.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">WELL STRUCTURED, DIRECT GUIDANCE</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
